                                <h4 class="font-bold text-yellow-900 dark:text-yellow-100 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">Why
                                    This Matters</h4>
                                <p class="text-base font-medium leading-relaxed text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200">
                                    The "Near Miss" effect on this machine—where you see "JOBS" just one click away from
                                    "ADDICTION"—mirrors the deceptive nature of FWFirst's marketing campaign. We are being sold the
                                    <em>possibility</em> of prosperity while the <em>probability</em> points to social cost.
                                </p>
                            </div>
